", "s": 62.02, "e": 62.38}, {"w": "a", "s": 62.38, "e": 62.54}, {"w": "part", "s": 62.54, "e": 62.7}, {"w": "-time", "s": 62.7, "e": 62.98}, {"w": "job", "s": 62.98, "e": 63.42}, {"w": "for", "s": 63.42, "e": 63.8}, {"w": "a", "s": 63.8, "e": 64.0}, {"w": "few", "s": 64.0, "e": 64.14}, {"w": "months", "s": 64.14, "e": 64.48}, {"w": "now.", "s": 64.48, "e": 64.88}]}, {"start": 67.92, "end": 70.06, "text": "What's the point of your argument?", "words": [{"w": "What's", "s": 67.92, "e": 68.68}, {"w": "the", "s": 68.68, "e": 68.84}, {"w": "point", "s": 68.84, "e": 69.12}, {"w": "of", "s": 69.12, "e": 69.4}, {"w": "your", "s": 69.4, "e": 69.58}, {"w": "argument?", "s": 69.58, "e": 70.06}]}, {"start": 73.08, "end": 75.94, "text": "They have different views on this matter.", "words": [{"w": "They", "s": 73.08, "e": 73.8}, {"w": "have", "s": 73.8, "e": 74.16}, {"w": "different", "s": 74.16, "e": 74.54}, {"w": "views", "s": 74.54, "e": 75.02}, {"w": "on", "s": 75.02, "e": 75.36}, {"w": "this", "s": 75.36, "e": 75.6}, {"w": "matter.", "s": 75.6, "e": 75.94}]}, {"start": 78.82, "end": 81.92, "text": "We have different opinions on that matter.", "words": [{"w": "We", "s": 78.82, "e": 79.54}, {"w": "have", "s": 79.54, "e": 79.86}, {"w": "different", "s": 79.86, "e": 80.28}, {"w": "opinions", "s": 80.28, "e": 80.88}, {"w": "on", "s": 80.88, "e": 81.3}, {"w": "that", "s": 81.3, "e": 81.56}, {"w": "matter.", "s": 81.56, "e": 81.92}]}, {"start": 85.1, "end": 88.9, "text": "He began to lose his sight when he was 70 years old.", "words": [{"w": "He", "s": 85.1, "e": 85.52}, {"w": "began", "s": 85.52, "e": 85.88}, {"w": "to", "s": 85.88, "e": 86.14}, {"w": "lose", "s": 86.14, "e": 86.4}, {"w": "his", "s": 86.4, "e": 86.68}, {"w": "sight", "s": 86.68, "e": 87.04}, {"w": "when", "s": 87.04, "e": 87.34}, {"w": "he", "s": 87.34, "e": 87.52}, {"w": "was", "s": 87.52, "e": 87.72}, {"w": "70", "s": 87.72, "e": 88.08}, {"w": "years", "s": 88.08, "e": 88.44}, {"w": "old.", "s": 88.44, "e": 88.9